[B]Welcome to the comprehensive accessories guide for the Samsung Galaxy Z Fold 7![/B]

This guide covers cases, screen protectors, chargers, and more - all with verified purchase links and up-to-date pricing.

[B]Device Highlights:[/B]
• 8.0" foldable inner display (film protectors only)
• 6.5" outer display (glass protectors OK)
• 4.2mm ultra-thin profile when unfolded
• Flex Hinge Pro (requires hinge-safe cases)
• S Pen support (Fold Edition)
• Under-display camera on inner screen

[B]Charging:[/B]
• Wired: 25W USB-PD
• Wireless: 15W Qi

